# Popover

Floating UI

Popover panels use `TxCard`; use `panelVariant/panelBackground/panelShadow/panelRadius/panelPadding` to control border, background, and shadow.


## Basic Usage

### Popover
:::TuffDemoWrapper{demo="PopoverPopoverDemo" code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <template>
    <TxPopover v-model="open">
      <template #reference>
        <TxButton>Click</TxButton>
      </template>

      Popover content
    </TxPopover>
  </template>
---
:::

