## API

### TxPopover Props

| Prop | Type | Default | Description |
|------|------|---------|------|
| `modelValue` | `boolean` | `false` | Description for modelValue. |
| `disabled` | `boolean` | `false` | Description for disabled. |
| `placement` | `PopoverPlacement` | `'bottom-start'` | Description for placement. |
| `offset` | `number` | `8` | Description for offset. |
| `width` | `number` | `0` | Description for width. |
| `minWidth` | `number` | `0` | Description for minWidth. |
| `maxWidth` | `number` | `360` | Description for maxWidth. |
| `referenceFullWidth` | `boolean` | `false` | Description for referenceFullWidth. |
| `showArrow` | `boolean` | `false` | Description for showArrow. |
| `arrowSize` | `number` | `12` | Description for arrowSize. |
| `motion` | `'fade' \| 'split'` | `'split'` | Description for motion. |
| `fusion` | `boolean` | `false` | Description for fusion. |
| `panelVariant` | `'solid' \| 'dashed' \| 'plain'` | `'solid'` | Text（TxCard variant） |
| `panelBackground` | `'blur' \| 'glass' \| 'mask'` | `'blur'` | Text（TxCard background） |
| `panelShadow` | `'none' \| 'soft' \| 'medium'` | `'soft'` | Text（TxCard shadow） |
| `panelRadius` | `number` | `18` | Description for panelRadius. |
| `panelPadding` | `number` | `10` | Description for panelPadding. |
| `closeOnClickOutside` | `boolean` | `true` | Description for closeOnClickOutside. |
| `closeOnEsc` | `boolean` | `true` | Description for closeOnEsc. |

### Events

| Event | Params | Description |
|------|------|------|
| `open` | - | Description for open. |
| `close` | - | Description for close. |
| `update:modelValue` | `boolean` | Description for update:modelValue. |
